.TH "vidioc_try_fmt_vid_cap" 9 "vidioc_try_fmt_vid_cap" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vidioc_try_fmt_vid_cap \- set video capture format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vidioc_try_fmt_vid_cap
.BI "(struct file *file "  ","
.BI "void *priv "  ","
.BI "struct v4l2_format *f "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "file" 12
descriptor of device
.IP "priv" 12
unused
.IP "f" 12
new format
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
new video format is set which includes width and
field type. width is fixed to 720, no scaling.
Only UYVY is supported by this hardware.
the minimum height is 200, the maximum is 576 (PAL)

return value: 0, no error

-EINVAL, pixel or field format not supported
